      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRUIKING (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 500m behind Who She Rules (28.96) in a T3 RSTW. Should bounce back. DOONGALLA ZIGGY (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Geelong over 460m behind Zari Desiree (26.74) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win. Placed at her previous run. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. KING OF CHAOS (3) has missed the frame the last couple but just a few runs back pushed the clock when winning over 425m at this track, taking a Maiden in a strong 23.97. Top win three back and rates a key player again. CORNHILL BOOMER (5) has top-three aspirations after placing at big odds last time.",
